@startuml
title ECO GUARDIAN - Comunicacao no Gameplay

object Jogador
object "update.js" as Update
object "player.js" as Player
object "boss.js" as Boss
object "level-builder.js" as LevelBuilder
object "state.js" as State
object "game-lifecycle.js" as Lifecycle

Jogador -> Update : 1: input (movimento/tiro/pause)
Update -> State : 2: validar estado atual
Update -> Player : 3: updatePlayer(scene)
Update -> Boss : 4: updateBoss(scene)
Update -> Boss : 5: bossAttackPlayer(scene)
Update -> LevelBuilder : 6: overlaps e progresso de fase
LevelBuilder -> Lifecycle : 7: triggerWin()/triggerEnd()
Lifecycle -> State : 8: alterar fim de jogo
@enduml
